title: TSM Biofrost montage

embed.description: WELCOME TO TSM BIOFROST MONTAGE A little montage I put together in my spare time. Hope you like it :D -------------------------------- This is a remake of the original Biofrost montage by Nicetryian. I changed it to my liking and I hope it is to your liking as well!

body: Hey there guys! This video is a remake of the original video and I would like to get some feedback on it! Such as what's good, what's bad, etc... Also feel free to subscribe and leave a like! It'd really help me out a lot :DD
